data.description: Absolutely gorgeous home located in the heart of Haymount. This 3 bedroom 1 and 1/2 bath home has been completely renovated just a couple years ago. The sellers put a new Trane HVAC in August of 2021, new plumbing on half of the house in February 2022. New garden window over the sink in the kitchen in 2023. Refinished hardwood floors throughout, living room with fireplace, dining room has built in corner cabinet, sunroom off the living room, and deck in the backyard. Walking distance to restaurants, coffee shops, boutiques, theatre and just a couple minutes from the ball park and downtown. Quick commute to Fort Liberty. This not only would be a perfect home for you to live in but would also make a wonderful Airbnb.
